### ===========================
### Service API
### ===========================

### Get all services
GET http://localhost:3000/api/services

### Create a service - 30 min consultation
POST http://localhost:3000/api/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "30 Min Consultation",
  "description": "Quick consultation session",
  "duration": 30,
  "price": 50
}

### Create a service - 60 min consultation
POST http://localhost:3000/api/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "60 Min Deep Consultation",
  "description": "In-depth consultation session",
  "duration": 60,
  "price": 100
}

### Create a service - invalid (missing name, should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "This should fail",
  "duration": 30,
  "price": 50
}